Position Property
This property is widely used for setting elements in diff diff positions

Types of Position
static - by default propert applied to elements
relative
absolute
fixed
sticky


Relative :
Keeping the current window in mind, we can change the position of image/element.
And the gap maintained from where the image/element is moved to new position
previous position space is maintained as it is

Properties: 
top
right
bottom
left

Absolute :
It is relative to its closest positioned ancestor
And gap is not maintained here

Properties are same as relative

Difference between fixed and sticky

fixed :
It behaves according to entire webpage

sticky :
It behaves/relative to parent element

